CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 21, 1961, pg. A15 reads: "Having Fun - This gay party appears to be having loads of fun. Seated, clockwise, are Robert French, Mrs. French, Thomas Augustine, Mrs. Augustine (partially hidden), Mrs. Alfred Hunt, Mr. Hunt, Mrs. Frank E. Bolden, Mr. Bolden, Mrs. Russell Washington and Mr. Washington."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, seated clockwise: Mr. and Mrs. Robert "Bob" P. French Jr., Mr. and Mrs. Thomas Augustine, Mr. and Mrs. Alfred Hunt, Mr. and Mrs. Frank E. Bolden, and Mr. and Mrs. Russell Washington, seated circular banquet table in Webster Hall for Alpha Phi Alpha Fall Fantasy Ball
